description: Dynamic Recursive CoT (DR-CoT). Dynamically decide when to recurse deeper vs. stop reasoning. Adaptive depth reasoning.
globs: []
alwaysApply: false
short_name: DRCoT
one_liner: recurse deeper only when needed during reasoning
